    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_40595dc8"><bpmn:text>Check exception in Art. 17 Abs. 3 lit. a&#10;Check exception in Art. 17 Abs. 3 lit. b&#10;Check exception in Art. 17 Abs. 3 lit. c&#10;Check exception in Art. 17 Abs. 3 lit. d&#10;Check exception in Art. 17 Abs. 3 lit. e&#10;No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_9a0ffd42"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_8039e023"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 18 Abs. 1, point 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_5d78b763"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Consent Withdrawn</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_2e224d27"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 21 Abs. 1&#10;No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Consent Withdrawn</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_71832f55"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 21 Abs. 1&#10;No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Legitimate Interest AND High Risk to Individuals AND Risk to Rights & Freedoms AND Consent Withdrawn</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_49a65d96"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Direct Marketing AND Consent Withdrawn</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_6a2ab819"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 21 Abs. 1&#10;No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Public Interest Processing AND Consent Withdrawn</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_36e87264"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 18 Abs. 1, point 2&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Processing Was Lawful</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_31476d18"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_9f2f5d47"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Perform without undue delay&#10;Applies when: Original Consent Given AND Data Subject Gave Consent</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
    <bpmn:textAnnotation id="Annotation_2f6f9135"><bpmn:text>No exception under Art. 17 Abs. 3&#10;No exception under Art. 12 Abs. 2&#10;No exception under Art. 11 Abs. 2&#10;Use reasonable effort&#10;Applies when: Information Made Public</bpmn:text></bpmn:textAnnotation>
